Combine peaches with orange juice, balsamic vinegar, cinnamon and mint, if desired. Add raspberries and mix gently. Set aside. Trim excess fat from pork chops. Combine thyme, rosemary, and Montreal Steak(R) Seasoning. Rub herb mixture on both sides of pork chops. Grill over medium heat for 5 to 7 minutes per side, or until done. To serve, spoon salsa over grilled chops.